  name: "Hammamet tour",
  info: "Hammamet is all about the beach. This is Tunisia's top sun-and-sea resort; a dreamy place dotted with pristine white buildings set beside a bright blue sea. The relaxing charms of this town woo all who come to sunbathe on the soft, white sand, with off-the-beach pursuits usually being nothing more strenuous than gentle strolls and a spot of shopping in the restored old town souks. It's a no stress kind of place that sums up the pleasures of Tunisia in one pretty package."
}, {
